==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Waul
<hw>Waul</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Of imitative
origin.]</ety> <def>To cry as a cat; to squall; to wail.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>wawl</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The helpless infant, coming <qex>wauling</qex> and crying into the
world.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waur</ent>⟦br⟧
